## Cloud Foundry Extension API
#
# This document describes the HTTP API exposed by the Steadybit Cloud Foundry extension.
#
## Landing
# The root endpoint reports the extension's capabilities.

###
GET http://localhost:8080
###

## Discovery
# The extension discovers Cloud Foundry applications via the CF V3 API.

### Target Description
###
GET http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app/discovery/target-description
###

### Attribute Descriptions
###
GET http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app/discovery/attribute-descriptions
###

### Discovery Description
###
GET http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app/discovery
###

### Discover Targets
###
GET http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app/discovery/discovered-targets
###

## Actions

### Stop App - Description
###
GET http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app.stop
###

### Stop App - Prepare
###
POST http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app.stop/prepare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": {
    "name": "my-app",
    "attributes": {
      "cloudfoundry.app.guid": ["abc-123"],
      "cloudfoundry.app.name": ["my-app"],
      "cloudfoundry.app.state": ["STARTED"]
    }
  },
  "config": {
    "duration": 60000
  }
}
###

### Stop App - Start
###
POST http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app.stop/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": {
    "AppGUID": "abc-123",
    "AppName": "my-app",
    "InitialState": "STARTED"
  }
}
###

### Stop App - Stop (rollback: restarts the app)
###
POST http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app.stop/stop
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": {
    "AppGUID": "abc-123",
    "AppName": "my-app",
    "InitialState": "STARTED"
  }
}
###

### Restart App - Description
###
GET http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app.restart
###

### Restart App - Prepare
###
POST http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app.restart/prepare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": {
    "name": "my-app",
    "attributes": {
      "cloudfoundry.app.guid": ["abc-123"],
      "cloudfoundry.app.name": ["my-app"]
    }
  },
  "config": {}
}
###

### Restart App - Start
###
POST http://localhost:8080/com.steadybit.extension_cloudfoundry.app.restart/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": {
    "AppGUID": "abc-123",
    "AppName": "my-app"
  }
}
###
